  "uuid": "tech-001-co-intelligence",
  "titulo": "Co-Intelligence: Living and Working with AI",
  "isbn": "978-0593716423",
  "sinopse": "Wharton professor Ethan Mollick provides guidance to help individuals thrive in the age of AI. He examines how to effectively partner with AI as a co-worker, co-teacher and coach while offering practical insights for preserving human identity and creating positive outcomes in this new era of human-AI collaboration.",
